# Make it easy for people to identify interactive elements

It must be possible for a person to know which element among multiple elements has the keyboard focus.

This is a requirement of:

<%= signpost_link("https://www.w3.org/WAI/WCAG21/Understanding/focus-visible", "WCAG 2.4.7 - Focus Visible (Level AA)", true)%>

<%= signpost_link("https://www.w3.org/WAI/WCAG21/Understanding/consistent-identification", "WCAG 3.2.4 - Consistent Identification (Level AA)", true)%>

